ARCHITECTURE.md
     1→# `sqlite-vec` Architecture
     3→Internal documentation for how `sqlite-vec` works under-the-hood. Not meant for
     4→users of the `sqlite-vec` project, consult
     5→[the official `sqlite-vec` documentation](https://alexgarcia.xyz/sqlite-vec) for
     6→how-to-guides. Rather, this is for people interested in how `sqlite-vec` works
     7→and some guidelines to any future contributors.
     8→
     9→Very much a WIP.
    10→
    11→## `vec0`
    13→### Shadow Tables
    49→### idxStr
    51→The `vec0` idxStr is a string composed of single "header" character and 0 or
    52→more "blocks" of 4 characters each.
    53→
    54→The "header" charcter denotes the type of query plan, as determined by the
    55→`enum vec0_query_plan` values. The current possible values are:
    56→
    57→| Name                       | Value | Description                                                            |
    58→| -------------------------- | ----- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------- |
