examples/sqlite3-cli/README.md
     1→# `sqlite-vec` statically compiled in the SQLite CLI
     3→You can compile your own version of the `sqlite3` CLI with `sqlite-vec` builtin.
     4→The process is not well documented, but the special `SQLITE_EXTRA_INIT` compile
     5→option can be used to "inject" code at initialization time. See the `Makefile`
     6→at the root of this project for some more info.
     7→
     8→The `core_init.c` file here demonstrates auto-loading the `sqlite-vec`
     9→entrypoints at startup.

examples/wasm/README.md
     1→# `sqlite-vec` statically compiled into WASM builds
     3→You can compile your own version of SQLite's WASM build with `sqlite-vec`
